              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14269221508715196330"><b>4.5 stars</b><br/><br/>I&apos;m sure I will revisit this again, possibly even quite soon. It&apos;s short but there is so much to unpack and it&apos;s so excellently written. I can see why this is a staple of Baldwin&apos;s oeuvre and one of the most influential non-fiction works of the last century.</span>
  <span id="freeText14269221508715196330" style="display:none"><b>4.5 stars</b><br /><br />I'm sure I will revisit this again, possibly even quite soon. It's short but there is so much to unpack and it's so excellently written. I can see why this is a staple of Baldwin's oeuvre and one of the most influential non-fiction works of the last century.</span>
