        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer897148228" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15499313250852020882">Nothing less than AWESOME! James Baldwin was a brilliant man and writer. I can&apos;t wait to get through all of his work. This is definitely a must read for everyone.</span>
  <span id="freeText15499313250852020882" style="display:none">Nothing less than AWESOME! James Baldwin was a brilliant man and writer. I can't wait to get through all of his work. This is definitely a must read for everyone.</span>
  <a data-text-id="15499313250852020882" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

